                    "image": "Sidebar_4_RelatedCreatures.png"
                },
                "html": "Myrucarxes rarely defer to any other creature, but they grudgingly acknowledge the authority of cabals of powerful myrucarxes dwelling in deep caverns on the <a aonid=\"288\" game-obj=\"Equipment\">Shadow Plane</a>. These cabals don't bother with the mundane work of terrorizing <a aonid=\"1\" game-obj=\"Planes\">Material Plane</a> cities; instead, they engage in worlds-spanning schemes to extinguish suns and create entire planets of cold, benighted horror."
            }
